Class LoadManager

java.lang.Object
cz.cvut.copakond.sweetfluffysheep.model.utils.json.LoadManager
public class LoadManager extends Object
LoadManager is responsible for loading data from a JSON object. It provides methods to retrieve various types of data, including booleans, integers, strings, and lists of integers with specific constraints.

    • getListOfListsWithDirFromDict

      public List<int[]> getListOfListsWithDirFromDict(String key, int[] limit, boolean canBeEmpty)

      limit - The limits for the coordinates.
      canBeEmpty - Whether the result can be empty.
